@startuml
title Diagrama de Comunicación - Gestión de Docentes
actor Admin
participant "DocenteController" as DC
participant "User Model / DB" as UserDB
participant "Docente Model / DB" as DocDB
participant "Role Model / DB" as RoleDB

Admin -> DC: POST /docentes (form)
DC -> UserDB: create user
UserDB --> DC: user
DC -> DocDB: create docente (user_id)
DC -> DocDB: create titulo
DC -> RoleDB: find 'docente'
DC -> RoleDB: attach role to user
DC --> Admin: redirect /docentes
@enduml
